<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Ganga_unibande_MHNT.jpg" class="image"></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Ganga_unibande_MHNT.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
Egg</div>
</div>
